data.description: Introducing an exceptional opportunity to own creekfront acreage, brimming with limitless potential & possibilities. This property is perfectly suited for a mini-farm or a family retreat, offering a tranquil setting sited within a mere 5-mile radius of Downtown Blue Ridge, Lake Blue Ridge, Toccoa River, & the renowned Aska Adventure Area. This barndominium's main level boasts the primary bedroom & a full bath, a bonus room, a spacious kitchen/dining area, a laundry room, a living room complete with a bar, an expansive pantry, and a well-appointed office space. Ascend to the upper level, where an expanse of unfinished space awaits, ideal for your extra storage or expansion. Additionally, the upper level presents an additional bedroom, a versatile bonus/rec area, & a full bath. Seamlessly integrated is a 2-car garage, along with an attached separate garage, tailored to accommodate all your needs for heavy equipment & yard maintenance. Also within this property is a 24x28 slab w a septic system already in place that resides right alongside the creek. Furthermore, an inviting small lake, complete w a charming dock, beckons to be enjoyed. A covered shed, another valuable asset within this property, offers refuge & protection for your belongings. The crowning jewel is an additional workshop that features that features central air, allowing you to engage in your artistic pursuits or woodworking endeavors comfortably.
